📖 Hafiz-e-Quran Khatm Card

A beautifully designed || Hafiz-e-Quran Khatm Card || to track the progress of Quran memorization and revisions (dora/khatm). This project is ideal for use by Huffaz, teachers, or institutions to organize and monitor Quran completion cycles.

---

📋 Features

- ✅ Track Juz (Sipara) completion status
- 🕋 Simple, clean, and elegant Islamic-themed design
- 🧠 Ideal for Hafiz-e-Quran students for daily or weekly khatam tracking
- 📥 Downloadable or printable format (if applicable)
- 📱 Mobile-friendly and responsive layout

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- || HTML5 || – For content structure  
- || CSS3 || – For styling and layout   

